Test Type	        File Name	                Purpose
Order Validation	CheckOrderValidation.java	Ensures orders are correctly processed
Pathfinding	        PathfindingTest.java	    Ensures A* algorithm computes correct paths
Performance	        PerformanceTest.java	    Measures execution time of route calculations
Stress Testing	    StressTest.java	            Ensures system can process 50+ orders concurrently
Edge Cases	        EdgeCaseTest.java	        Tests rare failures like GPS errors & no valid paths
Security	        SecurityTest.java	        Prevents unauthorized access to drone systems
CI Pipeline	        .github/workflows/ci.yml	Automates testing & enforces quality rules